==åç¨±ä¾†æº==
[[File:Imperial_Eagle_(Aquila_heliaca)_(38741311735).jpg|thumb]]å°±æ˜¯[[é˜¿å¥‘ç¾å°¼å¾·ç‹æœçš‡å®¶ç´‹ç« |é˜¿å¥‘ç¾å°¼å¾·ç‹æœçš‡å®¶ç´‹ç« ]]ä¸Šçš„é‚£éš»[[æ²™èµ«å·´èŒ²|æ²™èµ«å·´èŒ²]]ï¼Œé€™ç¨®çŒ›ç¦½ä¹Ÿåœ¨[[ä¼Šæœ—é«˜åŸ|ä¼Šæœ—é«˜åŸ]]ä¸Šæ£²æ¯ã€‚]]

Achaemenidä¸€è©çš„æ„æ€æ˜¯â€œAchaemenis/Achaemeneså®¶æ—ä¸­çš„ä¸€å“¡â€ï¼ˆå¤æ³¢æ–¯èªï¼šğƒğ§ğ ğ¶ğ´ğ¡ğ ÄHaxÄmaniÅ¡ï¼›<ref>{{cite book|ref=harv|last1=Curtis|first1=Vesta Sarkhosh|authorlink1=Vesta Sarkhosh Curtis|last2=Stewart|first2=Sarah|authorlink2=|title=The Sasanian Era|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=qPVHBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA79|year=2010|publisher=I.B.Tauris|isbn=978-0-85773-309-2}}</ref> æ˜¯{{link-en|bahuvrihiè¤‡åˆè©|bahuvrihi compound}}ï¼Œç¿»è­¯ç‚ºâ€œäº†è§£æœ‹å‹çš„æ€æƒ³â€ï¼‰ã€‚{{sfn|Tavernier|2007|p=17}} 

é˜¿å¥‘ç¾å°¼å¾·å¸åœ‹æ˜¯ç”±æ¸¸ç‰§çš„æ³¢æ–¯äººæ‰€å‰µå»ºã€‚â€œæ³¢æ–¯â€ä¸€è©æ˜¯å¤æ³¢æ–¯èªğ±ğ ğ¼ğ¿ï¼ˆPÄrsaï¼‰çš„å¸Œè‡˜èªå’Œæ‹‰ä¸èªç™¼éŸ³ï¼ŒæŒ‡çš„æ˜¯æºè‡ªå±…ä½åœ¨ä½©é‡Œæ–¯çš„äººæ‰€å»ºç«‹çš„åœ‹å®¶ã€‚<ref name=enc>{{cite book| author = Jamie Stokes| title = Encyclopedia of the Peoples of Africa and the Middle East, Volume 1| url = https://books.google.com/?id=Rtr7MQEACAAJ| year = 2009| publisher = Infobase Publishing| isbn = 978-0-8160-7158-6| pages = 2â€“3}} {{dead link|date=2019å¹´3æœˆ}}</ref>å¤æ³¢æ–¯èªXÅ¡ÄÃ§a({{lang|peo|{{script|Xpeo|ğ§ğğ‚}}}})çš„æ„æ€æ˜¯â€œå¸åœ‹â€ï¼Œé˜¿å¥‘ç¾å°¼å¾·äººç”¨ä¾†è¡¨é”ä»–å€‘æ˜¯ç”±å¤šå€‹æ°‘æ—çµ„æˆçš„åœ‹å®¶ã€‚<ref name=name>{{cite book|editor-last1=Daryaee |editor-first1=Touraj |last=Shapour Shahbazi|first=Alireza|author-link=Alireza Shapour Shahbazi |title=The Oxford handbook of Iranian history |url=https://archive.org/details/incompleteoxford00dary |url-access=limited |date=2012 |publisher=Oxford University Press |location=Oxford|isbn=978-0-19-973215-9|page=[https://archive.org/details/incompleteoxford00dary/page/n142 131]|quote=Although the Persians and Medes shared domination and others were placed in important positions, the Achaemenids did notâ€”could notâ€”provide a name for their multinational state. Nevertheless, they referred to it as Khshassa, "the Empire".|doi=10.1093/oxfordhb/9780199732159.001.0001}}</ref>

